            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "my daughter joined 6th Grade last year. As usual, adjusting to a new environment who shifted from US was worrying some. The way teachers and their COD Shravanya helped my daughter to settle in school is worth appreciation. The COD is one phone call away to solve all the concerns and support the child to take the right decision. The guidance that we received from school, with the help of Ms Shravanya, to choose the curriculum for grades 7 to 8 was huge. with patience, they heard our future plans for the child and guided us to. Well-balanced school without any frills. ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
